                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Sign up for Microsoft 365 Business Premium trial</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Create the new Microsoft 365 tenant</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Open web browser and go to: <strong>https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/business</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click the blue <strong>"See plans and pricing"</strong> button</li>
                                        <li>Find <strong>"Microsoft 365 Business Premium"</strong> and click <strong>"Try free for 1 month"</strong></li>
                                        <li>On the signup page, enter: <strong>admin@kompas-nordic.com</strong> (we'll set this up after domain verification)</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Set up account"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Choose <strong>"Set up a new business"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter business information:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>First name: Your name</li>
                                                <li>Last name: Your surname</li>
                                                <li>Business phone number: +31 6 1133 1118</li>
                                                <li>Company name: Kompas Nordic Netherlands</li>
                                                <li>Company size: 2-4 people</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Create a temporary tenant name: <strong>kompasnordic-nl</strong></li>
                                        <li>This will create: kompasnordic-nl.onmicrosoft.com</li>
                                        <li>Set up a strong password and save it in your password manager</li>
                                        <li>Complete phone verification when prompted</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Success indicator:</strong> You should see the Microsoft 365 admin center with a welcome message
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="warning-box">
                                        <strong>Important:</strong> Write down the tenant name (kompasnordic-nl.onmicrosoft.com) - you'll need this later!
                                    </div>
                                </div>
