                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Add custom domain (kompas-nordic.com)</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Connect the client's domain to Microsoft 365</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>In Microsoft 365 admin center, click <strong>"Settings"</strong> in the left menu</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Domains"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Add domain"</strong> button</li>
                                        <li>Type: <strong>kompas-nordic.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Use this domain"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Choose <strong>"I'll manage my own DNS records"</strong> (recommended)</li>
                                        <li>Microsoft will show you a TXT record to add</li>
                                        <li>Copy the TXT record details (something like: MS=ms12345678)</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <p><strong>Now add the DNS record:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Log into the domain registrar (GoDaddy, Namecheap, etc.)</li>
                                        <li>Find DNS settings or DNS management</li>
                                        <li>Look for option to add TXT record</li>
                                        <li>Add new TXT record:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Name/Host: @ (or leave blank)</li>
                                                <li>Value: The MS= code from Microsoft</li>
                                                <li>TTL: 3600 (1 hour)</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Save the DNS changes</li>
                                        <li>Go back to Microsoft 365 and click <strong>"Verify"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Wait up to 15 minutes for verification</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <div class="info-box">
                                        <strong>Verification may take time:</strong> DNS changes can take 15 minutes to 4 hours to propagate. Be patient!
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Configure DNS records for email</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Set up MX, SPF, DKIM, and DMARC records</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <p><strong>After domain verification, Microsoft will show you DNS records to add:</strong></p>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>1. MX Record (Mail Exchange):</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Name: @ (or leave blank)</li>
                                        <li>Value: kompas-nordic-com.mail.protection.outlook.com</li>
                                        <li>Priority: 0</li>
                                        <li>TTL: 3600</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>2. CNAME Records:</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>autodiscover ‚Üí autodiscover.outlook.com</li>
                                        <li>selector1._domainkey ‚Üí selector1-kompas-nordic-com._domainkey.kompasnordicnl.onmicrosoft.com</li>
                                        <li>selector2._domainkey ‚Üí selector2-kompas-nordic-com._domainkey.kompasnordicnl.onmicrosoft.com</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>3. TXT Records:</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>SPF: "v=spf1 include:spf.protection.outlook.com -all"</li>
                                        <li>DMARC: "v=DMARC1; p=none; rua=mailto:admin@kompas-nordic.com"</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    
                                    <div class="warning-box">
                                        <strong>Important:</strong> Add these records exactly as shown by Microsoft. The values might be slightly different for your tenant.
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Steps to add records:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to your domain registrar's DNS settings</li>
                                        <li>Add each record type (MX, CNAME, TXT) with the values provided</li>
                                        <li>Save all changes</li>
                                        <li>Wait 15-60 minutes</li>
                                        <li>Return to Microsoft 365 and click "Verify" for each record</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-group">
                    <div class="step-group-title">üë• User Account Creation</div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Create user accounts</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Add individual user accounts for each team member</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>In Microsoft 365 admin center, click <strong>"Users"</strong> in the left menu</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Active users"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Add a user"</strong> button</li>
                                        <li>Fill in user information:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>First name: John</li>
                                                <li>Last name: Smith</li>
                                                <li>Display name: John Smith</li>
                                                <li>Username: john.smith@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Password settings:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Choose <strong>"Let me create the password"</strong></li>
                                                <li>Create strong temporary password: TempPass2024!</li>
                                                <li>Check <strong>"Require this user to change their password when they first sign in"</strong></li>
                                                <li>Uncheck <strong>"Send password in email"</strong></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Product licenses:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Select location: <strong>Netherlands</strong></li>
                                                <li>Check <strong>"Microsoft 365 Business Premium"</strong></li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Optional settings: Add job title and department</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Finish adding"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Save the username and temporary password securely</li>
                                        <li>Repeat for each user</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Repeat this process for each user.</strong> Typical users for travel company:
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Manager: manager.name@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                            <li>Operations: operations.name@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                            <li>Sales: sales.name@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Create shared mailboxes</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Set up shared email addresses for departments</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>In Microsoft 365 admin center, go to <strong>"Teams & groups"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Shared mailboxes"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Add a shared mailbox"</strong></li>
                                        <li>For the first shared mailbox:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Name: Kompas Nordic Info</li>
                                                <li>Email address: info@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                                <li>Description: General information and inquiries</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Add"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click on the created shared mailbox to manage permissions</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Edit"</strong> next to Members</li>
                                        <li>Add users who should access this mailbox</li>
                                        <li>Set permissions:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><strong>Send As:</strong> Users who can send FROM this address</li>
                                                <li><strong>Send on behalf:</strong> Users who can send on behalf of this address</li>
                                                <li><strong>Read and manage:</strong> Users who can read emails</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Save changes"</strong></li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Repeat for each shared mailbox:</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>bookings@kompas-nordic.com (Booking inquiries)</li>
                                        <li>sales@kompas-nordic.com (Sales and partnerships)</li>
                                        <li>operations@kompas-nordic.com (Tour operations)</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    
                                    <div class="info-box">
                                        <strong>Shared mailboxes are free</strong> (up to 50GB) and don't require licenses for the mailbox itself, only for users accessing them.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
