                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to <strong>outlook.office.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Sign in with admin account: admin@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"New message"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Send test email TO: your personal email address</li>
                                        <li>FROM: admin@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                        <li>Subject: "Test - Microsoft 365 Setup"</li>
                                        <li>Message: "Testing email delivery from new Microsoft 365 setup"</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Send"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Check your personal email - should arrive within 5 minutes</li>
                                        <li>Reply to the test email from your personal account</li>
                                        <li>Check if reply arrives in Microsoft 365 mailbox</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Also test shared mailboxes:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>In Outlook, click your profile picture (top right)</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Open another mailbox"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Type: info@kompas-nordic.com</li>
                                        <li>Send test email from shared mailbox to external address</li>
                                        <li>Verify it's delivered and shows correct "From" address</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Success indicators:</strong>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Emails send without errors</li>
                                            <li>External recipients receive emails</li>
                                            <li>Replies come back to correct mailbox</li>
                                            <li>No delay longer than 5 minutes</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="warning-box">
                                        <strong>If emails don't work:</strong> Check DNS records again, wait longer for propagation, or contact Microsoft support.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
