            <div class="phase-content" id="phase-4-content">
                <div class="phase-summary">
                    <h4>What you'll accomplish:</h4>
                    <p>Create SharePoint sites for document storage and Microsoft Teams for collaboration, specifically organized for travel business operations.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-group">
                    <div class="step-group-title">üìÅ SharePoint Sites Creation</div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Create main company SharePoint site</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Set up central document hub for the company</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to <strong>admin.microsoft.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Show all"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"SharePoint"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Sites"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Active sites"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Create"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Choose <strong>"Team site"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Site name: <strong>"Kompas Nordic Netherlands"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Description: <strong>"Main document hub for Netherlands operations"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Privacy: <strong>"Private"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Language: <strong>"English"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Time zone: <strong>"Amsterdam, Berlin, Bern, Rome, Stockholm, Vienna"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Site owner: <strong>admin@kompas-nordic.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Finish"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Wait for site to be created (2-5 minutes)</li>
                                        <li>Click on site name to open it</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Success indicator:</strong> You can access the SharePoint site and see default document library
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
