                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="phase-content" id="phase-5-content">
                <div class="phase-summary">
                    <h4>What you'll accomplish:</h4>
                    <p>Set up Microsoft Intune to manage and secure all company devices (computers, phones, tablets) with automatic app deployment and security policies.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="step-group">
                    <div class="step-group-title">‚öôÔ∏è Intune Initial Setup</div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Enable and configure Microsoft Intune</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Turn on device management capabilities</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to <strong>endpoint.microsoft.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Sign in with admin account</li>
                                        <li>If prompted, click <strong>"Get started"</strong> to set up Intune</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Tenant administration"</strong> in left menu</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Tenant status"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Verify Intune service is <strong>"Active"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Customization"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Company Portal branding:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Company name: <strong>"Kompas Nordic Netherlands"</strong></li>
                                            <li>IT department name: <strong>"PAM Solutions IT Support"</strong></li>
                                            <li>IT department phone: <strong>+31 6 1133 1118</strong></li>
                                            <li>IT department email: <strong>support@pamsolutions.nl</strong></li>
                                            <li>Privacy statement URL: Leave blank for now</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Save"</strong></li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Success indicator:</strong> Intune dashboard loads and shows tenant status as "Healthy"
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Create device compliance policies</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Set security requirements for all devices</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <p><strong>Create Windows compliance policy:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>In Intune admin center, click <strong>"Devices"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Compliance policies"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Create Policy"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Platform: <strong>"Windows 10 and later"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Create"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Name: <strong>"Windows Security Requirements"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Description: <strong>"Basic security requirements for Windows devices"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Next"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Compliance settings:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Require BitLocker: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Firewall: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Antivirus: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>System security ‚Üí Password: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>System security ‚Üí Minimum password length: <strong>"6"</strong></li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Next"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Actions for noncompliance:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Mark device noncompliant: <strong>"Immediately"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Add action: <strong>"Block access to corporate resources"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Schedule: <strong>"1 day"</strong> after noncompliance</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Next"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Assignments: <strong>"All users"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Next"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Create"</strong></li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Create mobile device policy:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Create new policy for <strong>"iOS/iPadOS"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Name: <strong>"iOS Security Requirements"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Settings:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Jailbroken devices: <strong>"Block"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Passcode required: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Minimum passcode length: <strong>"6"</strong></li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <li>Repeat for <strong>"Android"</strong> platform</li>
                                        <li>Android settings:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Rooted devices: <strong>"Block"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Encryption: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Device security ‚Üí Screen lock: <strong>"Require"</strong></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="info-box">
                                        <strong>What this does:</strong> Devices must meet security requirements to access company email and files
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="step-group">
                    <div class="step-group-title">üì± Device Enrollment</div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Configure Windows Autopilot</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Set up automatic enrollment for new Windows devices</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Devices"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Windows"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Windows enrollment"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Devices"</strong> under Windows Autopilot</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Import"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Download the PowerShell script to collect hardware hashes</li>
                                        <li>On each Windows device, run PowerShell as Administrator:</li>
                                        <div class="code-snippet">Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned
Install-Script -Name Get-WindowsAutoPilotInfo
Get-WindowsAutoPilotInfo.ps1 -OutputFile AutoPilotHWID.csv</div>
                                        <li>Upload the CSV file in Intune</li>
                                        <li>Wait for sync (15-30 minutes)</li>
                                        <li>Create deployment profile:</li>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Click <strong>"Deployment profiles"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Click <strong>"Create profile"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"Windows PC"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Name: <strong>"Kompas Nordic Autopilot"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Convert all targeted devices: <strong>"Yes"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Deployment mode: <strong>"User-driven"</strong></li>
                                            <li>Join to Azure AD as: <strong>"Azure AD joined"</strong></li>
                                            <li>User account type: <strong>"Standard"</strong></li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <li>Assign to device group</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Create"</strong></li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Result:</strong> New devices automatically configure themselves when connected to internet
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Enroll existing Windows devices</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Add current company computers to management</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <p><strong>For each existing Windows device:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>On the device, go to <strong>Settings</strong> ‚Üí <strong>Accounts</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Access work or school"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Connect"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter work email: <strong>username@kompas-nordic.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Next"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter password and complete MFA if prompted</li>
                                        <li>Windows will download and apply policies</li>
                                        <li>Accept any permission requests</li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Done"</strong> when completed</li>
                                        <li>Restart the device</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Install Company Portal app:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go to Microsoft Store</li>
                                        <li>Search for <strong>"Company Portal"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Install the app</li>
                                        <li>Open Company Portal and sign in</li>
                                        <li>Complete device compliance check</li>
                                        <li>Follow any remediation steps if needed</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Verify enrollment in Intune:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Go back to <strong>endpoint.microsoft.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Click <strong>"Devices"</strong> ‚Üí <strong>"All devices"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Look for the device name</li>
                                        <li>Status should show <strong>"Compliant"</strong></li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="warning-box">
                                        <strong>Important:</strong> Have users save their work before starting - device may restart during enrollment
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Enroll mobile devices (iOS/Android)</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Add company phones and tablets to management</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <p><strong>For iOS devices:</strong></p>
