                                        <li>Download <strong>"Microsoft Intune Company Portal"</strong> from App Store</li>
                                        <li>Open the app</li>
                                        <li>Tap <strong>"Sign in"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter work email: <strong>username@kompas-nordic.com</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter password and complete MFA</li>
                                        <li>Tap <strong>"Get started"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Follow enrollment prompts</li>
                                        <li>When prompted, tap <strong>"Install"</strong> for management profile</li>
