                                        <li>Tap on management profile</li>
                                        <li>Tap <strong>"Install"</strong> and enter device passcode</li>
                                        <li>Return to Company Portal app</li>
                                        <li>Complete device compliance check</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>For Android devices:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Download <strong>"Microsoft Intune Company Portal"</strong> from Google Play</li>
                                        <li>Open the app</li>
                                        <li>Tap <strong>"Sign in"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Enter work credentials</li>
                                        <li>Tap <strong>"Begin"</strong></li>
                                        <li>Choose <strong>"Set up work profile"</strong> (recommended)</li>
                                        <li>Allow permissions for device management</li>
                                        <li>Complete enrollment process</li>
                                        <li>Install required apps from managed Google Play</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="info-box">
                                        <strong>Work Profile (Android):</strong> Creates separate space for work apps and data, keeping personal data private
                                    </div>
                                    
                                    <div class="success-box">
                                        <strong>Success indicator:</strong> Device appears in Intune admin center with "Compliant" status
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>
