                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="phase-content" id="phase-6-content">
                <div class="phase-summary">
                    <h4>What you'll accomplish:</h4>
                    <p>Migrate existing emails and files, train users, and successfully launch the new Microsoft 365 system with minimal business disruption.</p>
                    
                    <div class="danger-box">
                        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è CRITICAL - Before Starting Migration:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Complete backup of ALL existing data</li>
                            <li>Test restore procedures</li>
                            <li>Have rollback plan ready</li>
                            <li>Schedule during low-activity period</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
