                <div class="step-group">
                    <div class="step-group-title">üöÄ Go-Live Activities</div>
                    
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Final system testing</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Complete end-to-end testing before launch</div>
                            <details class="step-details">
                                <summary>Click for detailed step-by-step instructions</summary>
                                <div class="detailed-steps">
                                    <p><strong>Email Testing Checklist:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Send email from each user account to external address</li>
                                        <li>Send email from each shared mailbox</li>
                                        <li>Verify email signatures appear correctly</li>
                                        <li>Test email delivery time (should be under 5 minutes)</li>
                                        <li>Send email with attachment (PDF, Word doc)</li>
                                        <li>Test calendar invite to external client</li>
                                        <li>Verify mobile email works on each device</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>File Access Testing:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Access SharePoint from different devices</li>
                                        <li>Upload and download files</li>
                                        <li>Test file sharing with external email</li>
                                        <li>Verify mobile access to files</li>
                                        <li>Test OneDrive sync on all PCs</li>
                                        <li>Check permissions - users can only see what they should</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Teams and Collaboration:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Start video call between team members</li>
                                        <li>Share screen during meeting</li>
                                        <li>Record a meeting and verify playback</li>
                                        <li>Invite external person to Teams meeting</li>
                                        <li>Post messages in different channels</li>
                                        <li>Share file through Teams chat</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Security and Compliance Testing:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Verify MFA works for all users</li>
                                        <li>Test device compliance policies</li>
                                        <li>Check that non-compliant device is blocked</li>
                                        <li>Test app protection on mobile devices</li>
                                        <li>Verify data loss prevention policies</li>
                                        <li>Check audit logs are being generated</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <p><strong>Performance Testing:</strong></p>
                                    <ol>
                                        <li>Check email loading speed</li>
                                        <li>Test file sync speed</li>
                                        <li>Verify Teams video quality</li>
                                        <li>Check SharePoint search functionality</li>
                                        <li>Test mobile app performance</li>
                                    </ol>
                                    
                                    <div class="danger-box">
                                        <strong>Critical:</strong> Do not proceed to go-live if any critical functions are not working properly
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </details>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-checkbox" onclick="toggleStep(this)"></div>
                        <div class="step-content">
                            <div class="step-title">Execute go-live plan</div>
                            <div class="step-description">Launch the system during planned maintenance window</div>
